&lt;div style=&#34;display:inline-block;&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#39;http://sixmen.com/evernote/5a5a49b1-a403-40b2-9d0d-4b2b78670305.jpg&#39;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
